eep the momentum going. We need the next president to go 10x harder and keep deportationmaxxing to fix America.", "author": "AVeryNakedMan", "created": 1782966436557, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "hillaryforprison", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Trump is the first Republican president to even TRY to stop illegal immigration", "last_comment_created": 1782975923348, "content": "<p>The dude is literally the only guy in politics that is fighting for America.</p>\n<p>Reagan = gave amnesty to millions of invaders and turned California blue, permanently fucking America.</p>\n<p>Bush Sr. = did nothing to stop illegals.</p>\n<p>Bush Jr. = passed a border wall law and then DIDN'T FUND IT so it got built with literal scrap metal instead of a real barrier.</p>\n<p>Trump = Ended catch and release. Made a deal with Mexico to take back fake asylum seekers. Fully funded the border wall and is building it right now. Tried to end birthright citizenship for illegal aliens, something conservatives have wanted for decades.</p>\n<p>The dude is fighting for us, stop attacking him for not being perfect. Attack Democrats for actively trying to destroy America.</p>\n<p>And for fuck's sake, keep the momentum going. We need the next president to go 10x harder and keep deportationmaxxing to fix America.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 12, "score_up": 49, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4":